headline.print_headline: Birthday Ceremony for Ailing Thai King Canceled
headline.main: Birthday Ceremony for Ailing Thai King Canceled

lead_paragraph: A traditional birthday celebration ceremony for Thailand's King Bhumibol Adulyadej, the world's longest-reigning monarch, was canceled Friday because his doctors said he's not well enough to attend.
